column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.petroMag_r,p.i,p.petroMag_z,  p.petroR5#_r,p.petroR9#_r, p.petroR5#_z, p.petroR9#_z,   r.LOGD_#,r.LOGD_#Q, g.z FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecPhotoAll as s ON s.objid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecInfo as g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN RC3 AS r ON r.objid = p.objid
